name: Heart of Azeroth

main_spell_tooltip.description:
Your spells and abilities have a chance to activate Avatar for 35% of its base duration.

When the Vision of Perfection activates, you and up to 2 other nearby allies gain 4 Haste for 10 sec.

passive_spell_tooltip.description:
Reduces the cooldown of Avatar by 10.0%, and increases your Versatility by 3.

When you activate Avatar, immediately heal for 5% of maximum health.
Every 20 sec, gain a Null Barrier, absorbing 224 magic damage for 10 sec.

Every 2 sec, store 19 healing, up to a maximum of 1.4 million. When you dodge or parry an attack, heal for all stored healing.

The maximum health of all Tank specialization players in your party or raid is increased by 3%, stacking.

Unique:  Corruption Resistance increased by 10.

Azerite energy courses through your veins, increasing maximum health by 44 every 5 sec, stacking up to 10 times. While at maximum stacks, heal for 17 health every 5 sec.

Gain a stack of Anima of Life when you kill an enemy that yields experience or honor.

This effect is lost if you fall below 35% health.

spells.description: Equip: Harnesses the energy of raw Azerite, awakening exceptional pieces of armor that possess latent powers.

description: A living symbol of hope, borne by the champions of a dying planet. The fate of Azeroth will be shared by all her children.
